      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2,
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Active voice",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Most of the time, use active voice. It’s more direct and often uses fewer words than passive voice. In active voice, the subject performs the action. Active voice follows the pattern subject—verb—object.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Example: I (subject) drive (verb) the car (object).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "In passive voice, the subject receives the action. Passive voice follows the pattern subject—the verb “to be”—past participle—(and sometimes) object.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Example: The car (subject) is (the verb “to be”) driven (past participle) by me (object).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The car, which in the active voice is the object, is now the subject. In passive voice, who or what performs the action is often not stated.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Example: The car was driven.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "blockType": "text-editor"
}
